title: Duke, Lakers, Zion Williamson, and one and done players
itunes:title: Duke, Lakers, Zion Williamson, and one and done players
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb talks about Duke losing to Michigan State, one and done college players, what to expect from F Zion Williamson in the NBA, and who to blame for Los Angeles Lakers horrible season. Guests include Evan Daniels, Stephen Jackson, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
